[section#alg.random.sample
    [:en] Sample
    [:zh_CN] 抽样
]

[%@library sample]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<class PopulationIterator, class SampleIterator,
         class Distance, class UniformRandomBitGenerator>
  SampleIterator sample(PopulationIterator first, PopulationIterator last,
                        SampleIterator out, Distance n,
                        UniformRandomBitGenerator&& g);
[codeblock:end]

[enter:description]
[para:requires]
[list]
[item]
[:en] [`PopulationIterator] shall satisfy the requirements of an input iterator
([#input.iterators]).
[:zh_CN] [`PopulationIterator] 应当符合对输入迭代器的规定（[#input.iterators]）。

[item]
[:en] [`SampleIterator] shall satisfy the requirements of an output iterator
([#output.iterators]).
[:zh_CN] [`SampleIterator] 应当符合对输出迭代器的规定（[#output.iterators]）。

[item]
[:en] [`SampleIterator] shall satisfy the additional requirements of a random
access iterator ([#random.access.iterators]) unless [`PopulationIterator]
satisfies the additional requirements of a forward iterator
([#forward.iterators]).
[:zh_CN] 除非 [`PopulationIterator] 符合对前向迭代器的额外规定
（[#forward.iterators]），否则 [`SampleIterator] 应当符合对随机访问迭代器的额外
规定（[#random.access.iterators]）。

[item]
[:en] [`PopulationIterator][=']s value type shall be writable
([#iterator.requirements.general]) to [`out].
[:zh_CN] [`PopulationIterator] 的值类型应当可以向 [`out] 写出
（[#iterator.requirements.general]）。

[item]
[:en] [`Distance] shall be an integer type.
[:zh_CN] [`Distance] 应当为整数类型。

[item]
[:en] [`remove_reference_t<UniformRandomBitGenerator>] shall meet the
requirements of a uniform random bit generator type ([#rand.req.urng]) whose
return type is convertible to [`Distance].
[:zh_CN] [`remove_reference_t<UniformRandomBitGenerator>] 应当符合对均匀随机位
生成器类型的规定（[#rand.req.urng]），其返回类型可以转换为 [`Distance]。

[item]
[:en] [`out] shall not be in the range [=range(first,last)].
[:zh_CN] [`out] 应当处于范围 [=range(first,last)] 之内。
[list:end]

[para:effects]
[:en] Copies [`min(last - first, n)] elements (the [+sample]) from
[=range(first,last)] (the [+population]) to [`out] such that each possible
sample has equal probability of appearance.
[:zh_CN] 从 [=range(first,last)]（[+总体]）向 [`out] 复制
[`min(last - first, n)] 个元素（[+样本]），每个可能的样本均具有相等的出现概率。

[enter:note]
[:en] Algorithms that obtain such effects include [+selection sampling[%]] and
[+reservoir sampling[%]].
[:zh_CN] 能够体现这种效果的算法包括[+选择抽样[%]]和[+水塘抽样[%]]。
[exit:note]

[para:returns]
[:en] The end of the resulting sample range.
[:zh_CN] 结果的抽样范围的末尾。

[para:complexity]
[:en] [$[=O]([`last - first])].
[:zh_CN] [$[=O]([`last - first])]。

[para:remarks]
[list]
[item]
[:en] Stable if and only if [`PopulationIterator] satisfies the requirements of
a forward iterator.
[:zh_CN] 当且仅当 [`PopulationIterator] 满足前向迭代器的规定时为稳定算法。

[item]
[:en] To the extent that the implementation of this function makes use of random
numbers, the object [`g] shall serve as the implementation[=']s source of
randomness.
[:zh_CN] 在这个函数使用随机数的方面来说，对象 [`g] 应当作为该实现的随机性的来源。
[list:end]
[exit:description]
